Package one.microstream.persistence.types

Interface PersistenceDomain

public interface PersistenceDomain
(So far only a stub for the) conceptual type and ID consistency area. All runtimes belonging to a specific domain must fulfill the following conditions: - May not have different type definitions (but must not necessarily know all types of all other runtimes) - May not assign object ids that collide with assignments from other runtimes
